{"tid":1218861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你身邊既人只係無知而非弱智　請唔好放棄遊說佢地","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:03:04.000Z","uid":255759,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edc71bb567309ed090843557a4338cae6224ff67","tid":1218861,"uid":255759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"家中兩母就係無知份子之一<br />\n<br />\n雖然明白事理但平時接收資訊齋靠CCTVB<br />\n<br />\n當日我話去出去又叫我唔好搞咁多野又話我比人影響又盛<br />\n<br />\n眼見好多巴絲話同屋企人講政講唔通而避談政事<br />\n<br />\n但我心中總有份執著<br />\n<br />\n我唔想自己愛既屋企人係對前線義士冷嘲熱諷既一份子<br />\n<br />\n於是抽時間分別用左個零鐘出圖出片咁同佢地解析件事<br />\n<br />\n比佢地睇啲係CCTVB選擇性播放下睇唔倒既野<br />\n<br />\n最終成功將佢地既矛頭由示威者轉而指向警察<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例<span style=\"color: red;\">姑且</span>話可以有支持同反對既立場<br />\n<br />\n但面對警察毆打市民開槍爆頭呢啲大是大非既情況下<br />\n<br />\n多少有啲良心既人睇倒都唔應該支持<br />\n（以下附上小弟認為目前對遊說最有效既三條整合）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2019/06/13/3843727/20190612_news_17_new2AD_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2019%2F06%2F13%2F3843727%2F20190612_news_17_new2AD_w.mp4&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=33700f68\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2019/06/13/3843727/20190612_news_17_new2AD_w.mp4</a>　（蘋果剪輯合集　可下載）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=alnQjvISlxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DalnQjvISlxU&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=f4e13a20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=alnQjvISlxU</a> （Youtube剪輯合集）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/0evws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F0evws&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=7a7d3764\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/0evws</a>（前線母親勸說　可下載）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果有旁白 Youtube冇 自行取捨<br />\n第三條比啲做人阿媽睇既最有效<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實呢班無知者係一股好大的潛在力量<br />\n<br />\n周不時出黎同班師奶傾計總會人云亦云咁屌班後生暴力<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候一條片躂出黎會好有說服力<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊既人依舊處於無知狀態<br />\n<br />\n點醒一個得一個<span style=\"color: pink;\">（除非你知一講就會講到翻面 / 家嘈屋蔽）</span><br />\n<br />\n將條片傳上去啲家族群組再補多兩句都可以成為社會輿論既助力<br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲們唔好放棄身邊仲有得救既人"},{"pid":"b49d77828221494d620442804229eca4394ee54b","tid":1218861,"uid":255759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"如果你身邊既人只係無知而非弱智 請唔好放棄遊說佢地！"},{"pid":"f21267a38e054923033c329b355f29ec451537e4","tid":1218861,"uid":255759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:25:22.000Z","msg":"如果你身邊既人只係無知而非弱智 請唔好放棄遊說佢地！"},{"pid":"6be348f787b58916de56bd4eac4840461b683509","tid":1218861,"uid":255759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"如果你身邊既人只係無知而非弱智 請唔好放棄遊說佢地！"},{"pid":"58e89b6d5512a4bdee85ac574ad86c68f13e51e4","tid":1218861,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"已經同朋友反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 理性討論唔work嘅話可否歸類佢地為弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">To: 快要失去鬥志嘅一眾巴絲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">【當你迷茫絕望之時】我地到底係為咩而捨命抗爭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"b4e81fd9631734e089a2e13020cc9264aaca174c","tid":1218861,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e89b6d5512a4bdee85ac574ad86c68f13e51e4","tid":1218861,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"已經同朋友反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 理性討論唔work嘅話可否歸類佢地為弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">To: 快要失去鬥志嘅一眾巴絲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">【當你迷茫絕望之時】我地到底係為咩而捨命抗爭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n今次好輕易咁睇穿哂好多人智商水平"},{"pid":"c159312971ddbb424bc369e8259e9d773001fe85","tid":1218861,"uid":83025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:05:26.000Z","msg":"樓主可以說服兩老真係好好，adore"},{"pid":"9b2dbc95afe37b94ef4971a0f2f151b8992bc549","tid":1218861,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"最慘係對住只顧吃喝玩樂唔理事個班人<br />\n完全拒絕了解聆聽<br />\n你講完就hea鳩你<br />\n就算佢明都唔會理繼續自己去玩自撚私"},{"pid":"9ebe4daf1c829985fe4cc0980590dc41b007bbeb","tid":1218861,"uid":255759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e89b6d5512a4bdee85ac574ad86c68f13e51e4","tid":1218861,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"已經同朋友反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 理性討論唔work嘅話可否歸類佢地為弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">To: 快要失去鬥志嘅一眾巴絲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">【當你迷茫絕望之時】我地到底係為咩而捨命抗爭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:47:56.000Z","msg":"如果覺得排除討論講唔通呢點之外佢仲可以作為朋友既話<br />\n<br />\n就由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3513827bd96e00c953d60afec56eb38852f620f","tid":1218861,"uid":255759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c159312971ddbb424bc369e8259e9d773001fe85","tid":1218861,"uid":83025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite